Description: Interface around 'JDemetra+ 3.x' (<https://github.com/jdemetra/jdemetra-core>) seasonal adjustment software, STACE project.
 It offers access to several functions needed in other packages around 'JDemetra+ 3.x' and also some functions
 to compute general statistics on a time series.
